<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Page</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #74ebd5, #9face6);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .about-container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 30px;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .about-container h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-container p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.8;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .about-container a {
      display: block;
      margin: 30px auto 0;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      background: #74ebd5;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
      text-align: center;
      width: 200px;
    }

    .about-container a:hover {
      background: #67d8c4;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="about-container">
    <h1>About the Project</h1>
    <p>
      This project focuses on the development of a Nurse-Old Patient Allocation System, designed to revolutionize home healthcare by optimizing care delivery. 
      It provides an efficient and organized platform that facilitates seamless matching between patients and professional nurses, ensuring timely and personalized 
      care. By addressing accessibility and affordability challenges, the system empowers patients to receive quality treatment in the comfort of their homes.
    </p>
    <p>
      The application integrates advanced features such as role-based access control, secure data management, and scalability to accommodate a growing user base. 
      It not only enhances patient-centered care but also supports healthcare professionals by offering flexible work management tools. This innovative approach 
      aligns with the broader goal of transforming healthcare delivery systems to be more efficient, accessible, and cost-effective.
    </p>
    <p>
      By leveraging technology, the project aims to create significant social and economic impact, fostering better health outcomes, reducing costs, and 
      expanding job opportunities in the home healthcare sector. It stands as a testament to the potential of digital solutions in addressing modern 
      healthcare challenges.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
